<p><placeName>Lynchburgh </placeName>place not Valued</p>

<p>agreeably to the above request we have Valued the Property accordingly.</p>

<p><persName>Hugh McGarook</persName></p>

<p><persName>James Newell</persName></p>

<p><persName>Joseph Kent</persName></p>

<p>[Address:] <persName>Mr. Moses Austin Mercht</persName>. <placeName>on the Spanish Side of the
Mississippi Kaskaskia</placeName> Mail</p>

